com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce

Class MapSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.appengine.tools.mapreduce.MapSettings
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MapReduceSettings

    public class MapSettings
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Settings that affect how a Map job is executed. May affect performance and resource usage, but should not affect the result (unless the result is dependent on the performance or resource usage of the computation, or if different backends, modules or different base urls have different versions of the code).
